  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "When we use the local built SAIL El1 SW, the MD is not working fine with version"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "But when we use the elf generated with QC bare metal code, MD is up and running"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Failure logs with Local built SW:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Errors will come in UART like below and after this the UART in MD is non responsive"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Main%20domain%20not%20up%20with%20local%20SAIL%20EL1%20SW/image-2024-10-25_10-37-43.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
