    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Boot Process and dependency with SAIL"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "3.0 SAIL Boot sequence - XC-CT China - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Only SAIL Hypervisor has dependency with MD, EL1 SW has no dependency"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Test with Multicore Autosar hypervisor and SoC"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SoC version tested: rb-vcupro_main_dev_2024.42.5_userdebug."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "With the above SoC and SAIL El1 SW built in local with QC multicore hypervisor → MD runs properly with no reset, UART is responsive and displays are up"
    },
